timing_propag...ta_uncertainty(25.10)    timing_propag...ta_uncertainty(25.10)

Name
       timing_propagate_latch_data_uncertainty

Syntax
        timing_propagate_latch_data_uncertainty

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set to true, uses the clock phase associated with a flush latch's
       data pin as the "from" clock phase for  downstream  uncertainty  timing
       calculations

       When set to false, the downstream uncertainty calculations are based on
       the clock phase of the flush latch's clock signal.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

